## Introduction

KuttyPy apps can exchange data over local wifi. This is an experimental feature

+ Open the block coding interface on two phones
+ One of them will show a message at the top which will be something like `IP ADDRESS: PORT>KuttyPyChat` followed by a `connect` button
+ Press the connect button
+ Now both of them should show the message with `kuttypychat` replaced by `client` . They are connected and can exchange data.
+ Execute the programs and watch readings from one phone being sent to the other and vice versa


]]>
